    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Microvania 是一款微型银河战士恶魔城游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常小，屏幕分辨率只有 160x90！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它非常小，您也可以在一次游戏中完成游戏！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索 Micronus 星球的深处</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越并回溯精心制作的洞穴、丛林、实验室、废墟等像素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/980a254f13ecf5c0b07f168f1d1d29ff.poster.avif?t=1766555155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/980a254f13ecf5c0b07f168f1d1d29ff.webm?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/980a254f13ecf5c0b07f168f1d1d29ff.mp4?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几乎每个房间都有隐藏的物品或秘密路径。你能找到它们吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找并利用经典的升级比喻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/6647755d4a787007a411448016758ee6.poster.avif?t=1766555155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/6647755d4a787007a411448016758ee6.webm?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/6647755d4a787007a411448016758ee6.mp4?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >导弹、爪子、球模式等等！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义你的游戏风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/3dc164e1c69b30b77022cc84ca0ea82c.poster.avif?t=1766555155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/3dc164e1c69b30b77022cc84ca0ea82c.webm?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/3dc164e1c69b30b77022cc84ca0ea82c.mp4?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>装备微型卡来修改你的武器和能力。创造你自己的游戏风格。只要确保你找到了足够的微型电池来为它们供电即可。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Microvania 尊重你的时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/f9cb70686949fc0b3d93d33f009757b7.poster.avif?t=1766555155\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/f9cb70686949fc0b3d93d33f009757b7.webm?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/f9cb70686949fc0b3d93d33f009757b7.mp4?t=1766555155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不用担心保存你的进度——每次你进入房间时，游戏都会创建一个检查点，如果你死了，你会回到这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >退出主菜单将保存你所在位置的游戏，这样你就可以在下一个会话中直接返回。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可访问性和完全控制器支持</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/70b93cdf089de999994b6f7a7fb6efbd.avif?t=1766555155\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为控制器设计，具有完全可定制的按钮。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/c88539d76af05b767cc79f565b0d9f70.webp?t=1766555155\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114890/extras/c88539d76af05b767cc79f565b0d9f70.poster.avif?t=1766555155\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=360 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括辅助功能选项，例如快速射击或各种功能的切换模式。如果boss给你带来麻烦，你可以使用“在Boss处重生”设置，让战斗更容易。</p>",
